  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">KPMG - SANRU Internal Management and Control</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">KPMG - SANRU Internal Management and Control</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Denna insats avser ett uppdrag som gavs till KPMG Sverige f&#xF6;r att g&#xF6;ra en &#xF6;versyn av Sanrus internstyrnings- och kontrollsystem. Sanru har ans&#xF6;kt om st&#xF6;d till ett projekt som syftar till att f&#xF6;rb&#xE4;ttra f&#xF6;rlossningsv&#xE5;rden i tv&#xE5; provinser.
Sanru &#xE4;r en nationell NGO i DRK som inte har haft n&#xE5;got samarbete med ambassaden tidigare. D&#xE4;rf&#xF6;r fick KPMG f&#xF6;r uppgift att genomf&#xF6;ra ett &#xF6;versyn av Sanrus interna system.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This contribution concerns an assignment given to KPMG Sweden to perform a review of Sanru&apos;s internal management and control systems.
Sanru is a national NGO in DRC that has approached the Embassy to seek support for a project aimed at improving maternal care. Since the embassy has no previous experience of collaborating with working with Sanru, a review of internal management and control systems was required. This assignment was therefore given to KPMG Sweden.</narrative>
  </description>
